<MudText Typo="@Typo.h5">
    Knowledge Checks
</MudText>

<br />

<MudText Typo="@Typo.body1">
    Knowledge Checks are Skill Checks that are used to determine how well you know a particular subject tied to a specific Skill.
    <br />
    <br />
    Detailed information about Knowledge Checks can be found in the <MudLink Href="/core-rules/actions-reactions">Actions & Reactions</MudLink> section.
</MudText>

